<p>Is it possible to change the path where the pkgIndex.tcl can be found to wrap a starkit?</p>  <p>The standart is that the pkgIndex.tcl is at the top in the app like this:</p>  <pre><code>hello.vfs |-- main.tcl `-- lib     `-- app-hello         |-- hello.tcl         `-- pkgIndex.tcl </code></pre>  <p>I want to change the path so a construct like this is possible:</p>  <pre><code>hello.vfs |-- main.tcl `-- lib     `-- app-hello         |-- hello.tcl         `-- tcl             `-- pkgIndex.tcl </code></pre>